                "invention-title": [
                    "Ammonia synthesis and hydrogen metallurgical coupling co-production system and method based on free piston Stirling ultra-high temperature heat pump",
                    "基于自由活塞斯特林超高温热泵的氨合成与氢冶金耦合联产系统及方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to the technical field of hydrogen metallurgy, in particular to an ammonia synthesis and hydrogen metallurgy coupling co-production system and method based on a free piston Stirling ultra-high temperature heat pump. The invention provides an ammonia synthesis and hydrogen metallurgy coupling co-production system based on a free piston Stirling ultra-high-temperature heat pump. The ammonia synthesis and hydrogen metallurgy coupling co-production system comprises an ammonia synthesis device, the free piston Stirling ultra-high-temperature heat pump and a hydrogen metallurgy reaction furnace. The free piston Stirling ultrahigh-temperature heat pump is provided with a low-temperature heat exchanger and a high-temperature heat The ammonia synthesis device is provided with a first heat exchanger which is connected with the low-temperature heat exchanger through a first heat exchange medium pipeline; the hydrogen metallurgy reaction furnace is provided with a second heat exchanger, and the second heat exchanger is connected with the high-temperature heat exchanger through a second heat exchange medium pipeline. According to the ammonia synthesis and hydrogen metallurgy coupling co-production system and method based on the free piston Stirling ultra-high-temperature heat pump, reaction waste heat in the ammonia synthesis process can be effectively utilized, heat energy loss is reduced, and the problems that in the prior art, the hydrogen metallurgy process is low in efficiency and high in cost can be solved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及氢冶金技术领域，具体涉及基于自由活塞斯特林超高温热泵的氨合成与氢冶金耦合联产系统及方法。本发明提供的基于自由活塞斯特林超高温热泵的氨合成与氢冶金耦合联产系统，包括氨合成装置、自由活塞斯特林超高温热泵和氢冶金反应炉；自由活塞斯特林超高温热泵设置有低温换热器和高温换热器；氨合成装置设置有第一换热器，第一换热器与低温换热器通过第一换热介质管路连接；氢冶金反应炉设置有第二换热器，第二换热器与高温换热器通过第二换热介质管路连接。本发明的基于自由活塞斯特林超高温热泵的氨合成与氢冶金耦合联产系统及方法，能有效利用氨合成工艺中反应余热，减少热能损耗，能够克服现有技术中氢冶金工艺效率低、成本高的问题。"
                }
            ]
